dct_title_s: Insurance maps of Newark, New Jersey : volume three (Sheet 240)
dct_description_sm: Includes contour map, key, streets and specials index, and text. "5285." Contour map sheet has title: Contour map of Newark, New Jersey, showing the distributing reservoirs of the city water works and the districts supplied by each. Sheets 201-273 of: Insurance maps of Newark, New Jersey, vol. 1-4.
dct_publisher_sm: New York : Sanborn-Perris Map Co., Limited 1892.
